            <div>
                <head>“TO A BROWN BOY”</head>
                
                
                <lg>
                <lg type="quatrain">
                    <l enjamb="no">That <rs theme="race">brown</rs> <rs theme="child">girl’s</rs> swagger gives a <rhyme type="A">twitch</rhyme></l>
                    <l enjamb="no">To beauty like a <rhyme type="B">queen</rhyme>;</l>
                    <l enjamb="no">Lad, never dam your <rs theme="body">body’s</rs> <rhyme type="A">itch</rhyme></l>
                    <l enjamb="no">When <rs theme="love">loveliness</rs> is <rhyme type="B">seen</rhyme>.</l>
                </lg>
                </lg>
                
                
                <lg>
                <lg type="quatrain">
                    <l enjamb="no">For there is ample room for <rhyme type="C">bliss</rhyme></l>
                    <l enjamb="no">In pride in clean, <rs theme="race">brown</rs> <rhyme type="D"><rs theme="body">limbs</rs></rhyme>,</l>
                    <l enjamb="no">And <rs litDevice="personification"><rs theme="body">lips</rs> know</rs> better how to <rhyme type="C">kiss</rhyme></l>
                    <l enjamb="no">Than how to raise <rs theme="race">white</rs><rhyme type="D"><rs theme="religion">hymns</rs></rhyme>.</l>
                </lg>
                </lg>
                
                
                <lg>
                <lg type="quatrain">
                    <l enjamb="no">And when your <rs theme="body">body’s</rs> death gives <rhyme type="E">birth</rhyme></l>
                    <l enjamb="no">To soil for spring to <rhyme type="F">crown</rhyme>,</l>
                    <l enjamb="no"><rs theme="male">Men</rs> will not ask if that rare <rhyme type="E">earth</rhyme></l>
                    <l enjamb="no">Was <rs theme="race">white</rs> flesh once, or <rhyme type="F"><rs theme="race">brown</rs></rhyme>.</l>   
                </lg>
                </lg>
                <byline>Countée Cullen</byline>
            </div>
        </body>
